reviewText: This video is well designed for the average person to use in butchering ,good job in making this product. Thanks you.

It tells me everything I wanted to know and explained even more cuts than I wanted to learn about.  Made cutting up these two steers go MUCH faster. It has a real home made quality BUT the show and tell makes it easy to follow. We also purchansed 'The Art of Beef Cutting: A meat Professional's Guide to Butchering' to help as we were cutting.
